k hotel.0 aThe "I"s of Robert Silverberg -- Foreword -- Ishmael in love -- Going down smooth -- The reality trip -- The songs of summer -- The Martian invasion journals of Henry James -- Push no more -- House of bones -- Call me Titan -- Our lady of the Sauropods -- There was an old woman -- The dybbuk of Mazel Tov IV -- Caliban -- Passengers -- Now plus N, now minus N -- The iron star -- The Science Fiction Hall of Fame -- The secret sharer -- To see the invisible man. 0aShort stories, American. 4aScience fiction. 4aShort stories. 7aShort stories, American.2fast0(OCoLC)fst01117064 7aScience fiction.2fast0(OCoLC)fst01726489 7aShort stories.2fast0(OCoLC)fst01726740 7aScience fiction.2gsafd 7aShort stories.2gsafd 7aScience fiction.2lcgft 7aShort stories.2lcgft1 aScalzi, John,d1969-ewriter of introduction.12aSilverberg, Robert.tIshmael in love.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tGoing down smooth.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tReality trip.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tSongs of summer.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tMartian invasion journals of Henry James.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tPush no more.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tHouse of bones.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tCall me Titan.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tOur Lady of the sauropods.iContainer of (work) :12aSilverberg, Robert.tThere was an old woman.iContainer of (work) :  apc17 2017-03-29axn11 2017-12-14 1 copy rec'd., to USPRLL